<!--
Sprint 4 P0-2 (2026-06-07): Mac launchd plist for 芙清 DuckDB 每日备份
Sprint 10 B3 (2026-06-08): 失败 loud-fail (脚本内置 osascript + mail)
                              改 BJ 日期命名 (跟用户日历日期一致, 之前 UTC 错叫)

复用 com.fuqing.backup-cleanup.weekly.plist 模式 (Sprint 1 治理留下)

安装:
  cp com.fuqing.duckdb-backup.daily.plist ~/Library/LaunchAgents/
  launchctl unload ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.fuqing.duckdb-backup.daily.plist 2>/dev/null
  launchctl load ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.fuqing.duckdb-backup.daily.plist
  launchctl list | grep fuqing.backup   验证加载 (2 个服务: daily + weekly cleanup)

卸载:
  launchctl unload ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.fuqing.duckdb-backup.daily.plist
  rm ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.fuqing.duckdb-backup.daily.plist

设计:
  每日 03:30 跑（避开 ETL 跑批窗口 08:30 + 错开 weekly cleanup 周日 03:00）
  scripts/etl/backup_duckdb.py 用 shutil.copy2 复制 + zstd 压缩
  7 天保留由 com.fuqing.backup-cleanup.weekly.plist 兜底
  stdout/stderr 重定向到 /tmp/fuqing-duckdb-backup.log
  失败 loud-fail: 脚本内置 osascript 桌面通知 + mail 发到 hutou@fuqing.local
  exit code != 0 触发 launchd 自动通知
-->
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<dict>
    <key>Label</key>
    <string>com.fuqing.duckdb-backup.daily</string>

    <key>ProgramArguments</key>
    <array>
        <string>/Users/hutou/homebrew/bin/python3</string>
        <string>/Users/hutou/Desktop/fuqin date/fuqing-crm-analytics/scripts/etl/backup_duckdb.py</string>
    </array>

    <key>WorkingDirectory</key>
    <string>/Users/hutou/Desktop/fuqin date/fuqing-crm-analytics</string>

    <key>StartCalendarInterval</key>
    <dict>
        <key>Hour</key>
        <integer>3</integer>
        <key>Minute</key>
        <integer>30</integer>
    </dict>

    <key>StandardOutPath</key>
    <string>/tmp/fuqing-duckdb-backup.log</string>

    <key>StandardErrorPath</key>
    <string>/tmp/fuqing-duckdb-backup.log</string>

    <key>RunAtLoad</key>
    <false/>
</dict>
</plist>
